- Stanford课程: Math 256 (Algebraic Number Theory)
- Princeton课程: MAT 420 (Algebraic Number Theory)
- MIT课程: 18.785 (Number Theory I)
- Metamath: [L-Function](http://us.metamath.org/mpeuni/df-lfunction.html)

